<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>내 페르소나 — livere.ai</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syne:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;500;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --bg:     #080b14;
  --s1:     #0d1120;
  --s2:     #121828;
  --s3:     #182038;
  --s4:     #1e2844;

  --cyan:   #22d3ee;
  --violet: #a78bfa;
  --green:  #4ade80;
  --amber:  #fbbf24;
  --pink:   #f472b6;
  --red:    #f87171;
  --blue:   #60a5fa;

  --t1: #f0f4ff;
  --t2: #8899bb;
  --t3: #3d4f72;

  --border:  rgba(255,255,255,.07);
  --border2: rgba(255,255,255,.13);

  --sans:    'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
  --display: 'Syne', sans-serif;
  --mono:    'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
}

* { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box }
html { scroll-behavior: smooth }
body {
  font-family: var(--sans);
  background: var(--bg);
  color: var(--t1);
  min-height: 100vh;
  overflow-x: hidden;
}

/* ── MESH BG ── */
body::before {
  content: '';
  position: fixed; inset: 0; pointer-events: none; z-index: 0;
  background:
    radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 50% at 15% 10%, rgba(34,211,238,.05) 0%, transparent 60%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 40% at 85% 80%, rgba(167,139,250,.05) 0%, transparent 60%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 30% at 50% 50%, rgba(96,165,250,.03) 0%, transparent 70%);
}

/* ── TOPBAR ── */
.topbar {
  position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 200;
  height: 54px;
  background: rgba(8,11,20,.92);
  backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  display: flex; align-items: center;
  padding: 0 28px; gap: 0;
}
.brand {
  font-family: var(--display);
  font-size: 15px; font-weight: 800;
  letter-spacing: .04em;
  color: var(--cyan);
  margin-right: 28px;
}
.nav-links { display: flex; gap: 4px }
.nav-link {
  font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--t3); padding: 6px 14px;
  border-radius: 7px; cursor: pointer;
  transition: all .15s; text-decoration: none;
}
.nav-link:hover { color: var(--t2); background: rgba(255,255,255,.04) }
.nav-link.active { color: var(--t1); background: rgba(255,255,255,.07) }
.topbar-right {
  margin-left: auto;
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
}
.weight-pill {
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
  background: rgba(34,211,238,.08);
  border: 1px solid rgba(34,211,238,.22);
  border-radius: 20px; padding: 5px 14px;
}
.wp-label { font-size: 10px; color: var(--t2); letter-spacing: .1em; text-transform: uppercase }
.wp-val   { font-family: var(--display); font-size: 18px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--cyan) }
.settings-btn {
  background: var(--s2); border: 1px solid var(--border2);
  color: var(--t2); padding: 7px 14px;
  border-radius: 8px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600;
  cursor: pointer; transition: all .15s;
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
}
.settings-btn:hover { border-color: var(--violet); color: var(--violet) }

/* ── LAYOUT ── */
.page { position: relative; z-index: 1; padding: 32px 28px; max-width: 1280px; margin: 0 auto }

/* ── PROFILE HERO ── */
.profile-hero {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 280px 1fr 240px;
  gap: 20px;
  margin-bottom: 28px;
}

/* avatar card */
.avatar-card {
  background: var(--s1);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 16px;
  padding: 28px 20px;
  display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;
  gap: 14px;
  position: relative; overflow: hidden;
}
.avatar-card::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 3px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--cyan), var(--violet));
}
.avatar-ring-wrap { position: relative; width: 110px; height: 110px }
.avatar-ring-svg  { position: absolute; inset: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; transform: rotate(-90deg) }
.avatar-face {
  position: absolute; inset: 12px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--s2), var(--s3));
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  font-size: 40px;
}
.avatar-pct {
  font-family: var(--display);
  font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: .12em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--t3);
  margin-top: -4px;
}
.avatar-pct strong { color: var(--cyan); font-size: 18px; display: block }
.avatar-name { font-family: var(--display); font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700 }
.avatar-sub  { font-size: 11px; color: var(--t3); text-align: center; line-height: 1.6 }

.avatar-badges {
  display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 5px; justify-content: center;
}
.badge {
  font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .08em;
  padding: 3px 9px; border-radius: 10px;
}
.badge.verified { background: rgba(74,222,128,.12); color: var(--green); border: 1px solid rgba(74,222,128,.25) }
.badge.pro      { background: rgba(167,139,250,.12); color: var(--violet); border: 1px solid rgba(167,139,250,.25) }

/* identity card */
.identity-card {
  background: var(--s1); border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 16px; padding: 24px 26px;
  display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px;
}
.ic-title {
  font-family: var(--display); font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: .08em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--t3);
  margin-bottom: 4px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
}
.ic-title::after { content: ''; flex: 1; height: 1px; background: var(--border) }

.identity-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 12px }
.id-item {}
.id-label { font-size: 10px; color: var(--t3); letter-spacing: .1em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 3px }
.id-val   { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--t1); line-height: 1.4 }
.id-val.empty { color: var(--t3); font-weight: 400; font-size: 12px }
.id-val .lit { color: var(--cyan) }

.career-timeline { margin-top: 4px }
.ct-item {
  display: flex; gap: 14px; align-items: flex-start;
  padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
}
.ct-item:last-child { border-bottom: none }
.ct-dot {
  width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--cyan); flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 5px;
  box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--cyan);
}
.ct-dot.past { background: var(--t3); box-shadow: none }
.ct-body { flex: 1 }
.ct-period { font-size: 10px; color: var(--t3); margin-bottom: 2px; font-family: var(--mono) }
.ct-role   { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--t1) }
.ct-sub    { font-size: 11px; color: var(--t2); margin-top: 1px }
.ct-badge  {
  font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700;
  padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 8px;
  background: rgba(34,211,238,.1); color: var(--cyan);
  align-self: center; flex-shrink: 0;
}

/* weight card */
.weight-card {
  background: var(--s1); border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 16px; padding: 22px 18px;
  display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 14px;
}
.wc-title {
  font-family: var(--display); font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: .1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--t3);
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
}
.wc-title::after { content: ''; flex: 1; height: 1px; background: var(--border) }

.weight-total {
  text-align: center;
  background: rgba(34,211,238,.06);
  border: 1px solid rgba(34,211,238,.18);
  border-radius: 12px; padding: 16px;
}
.wt-val { font-family: var(--display); font-size: 36px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--cyan) }
.wt-label { font-size: 10px; color: var(--t2); margin-top: 3px }

.weight-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px }
.wr-dot  { width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0 }
.wr-name { font-size: 11px; color: var(--t2); flex: 1 }
.wr-bar-wrap { flex: 2; height: 4px; background: rgba(255,255,255,.05); border-radius: 2px; overflow: hidden }
.wr-bar  { height: 100%; border-radius: 2px; transition: width 1.2s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1) }
.wr-val  { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; width: 34px; text-align: right }

.weight-note {
  font-size: 10px; color: var(--t3); line-height: 1.7;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,.03); border-radius: 8px; padding: 10px 12px;
}

/* ── NODE GRID ── */
.section { margin-bottom: 24px }
.section-head {
  font-family: var(--display); font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: .1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--t3);
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 14px;
}
.section-head::after { content: ''; flex: 1; height: 1px; background: var(--border) }
.section-sub { font-size: 11px; color: var(--t3); font-family: var(--sans); text-transform: none; letter-spacing: 0; font-weight: 400 }

.node-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr); gap: 10px }

.node-card {
  background: var(--s1); border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 12px; padding: 16px 14px;
  cursor: pointer; transition: all .2s;
  position: relative; overflow: hidden;
}
.node-card.lit {
  border-color: rgba(34,211,238,.28);
}
.node-card.lit::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 2px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--nc-color, var(--cyan)), transparent);
}
.node-card.dim { opacity: .38; filter: grayscale(.4) }
.node-card:hover { border-color: var(--border2); transform: translateY(-1px) }
.node-card.lit:hover { border-color: rgba(34,211,238,.45) }

.nc-status {
  position: absolute; top: 10px; right: 10px;
  width: 7px; height: 7px; border-radius: 50%;
}
.nc-status.on  { background: var(--nc-color, var(--cyan)); box-shadow: 0 0 6px var(--nc-color, var(--cyan)) }
.nc-status.off { background: var(--t3) }

.nc-icon  { font-size: 22px; margin-bottom: 8px }
.nc-label { font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: .1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--t3); margin-bottom: 5px }
.nc-val   { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--t1); line-height: 1.4 }
.nc-val.empty { color: var(--t3); font-size: 11px; font-weight: 400 }
.nc-sub   { font-size: 10px; color: var(--t3); margin-top: 4px }

/* ── INFLUENCE / INTERESTS ── */
.two-col { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px }

.stat-card {
  background: var(--s1); border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 14px; padding: 20px 22px;
}

/* interest tags */
.interest-wrap { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 7px; margin-top: 8px }
.int-tag {
  font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; padding: 5px 12px;
  border-radius: 12px; cursor: pointer; transition: all .2s;
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
}
.int-tag:hover { transform: translateY(-1px) }
.int-dot { width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0 }

/* agenda activity */
.agenda-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; margin-top: 8px }
.agenda-item {
  background: var(--s2); border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 10px; padding: 12px 14px;
  display: flex; gap: 12px; align-items: center;
  cursor: pointer; transition: border-color .15s;
}
.agenda-item:hover { border-color: var(--border2) }
.ai-stance {
  font-size: 10px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: .08em;
  padding: 3px 9px; border-radius: 8px; flex-shrink: 0;
}
.stance-against { background: rgba(248,113,113,.12); color: var(--red) }
.stance-for     { background: rgba(74,222,128,.12);  color: var(--green) }
.stance-neutral { background: rgba(96,165,250,.12);  color: var(--blue) }
.ai-keywords { flex: 1; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--t1); line-height: 1.4 }
.ai-meta     { font-size: 10px; color: var(--t3); margin-top: 2px }
.ai-vol      { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 11px; color: var(--t2); flex-shrink: 0; text-align: right }
.ai-weight   { font-family: var(--display); font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--amber); flex-shrink: 0 }

/* influence spider */
.spider-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr; gap: 20px; align-items: center }
.spider-svg-wrap { width: 180px; height: 180px }

.inf-bars { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px }
.ib-row   { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px }
.ib-dot   { width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0 }
.ib-name  { font-size: 11px; color: var(--t2); width: 80px; flex-shrink: 0 }
.ib-bar-wrap { flex: 1; height: 5px; background: rgba(255,255,255,.05); border-radius: 3px; overflow: hidden }
.ib-bar   { height: 100%; border-radius: 3px; transition: width 1.4s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1) }
.ib-val   { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; width: 36px; text-align: right }

/* ── CONSENT LOG MINI ── */
.consent-mini {
  background: var(--s1); border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 14px; padding: 20px 22px;
}
.log-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; margin-top: 10px }
.log-item {
  display: flex; gap: 12px; align-items: center;
  padding: 9px 12px; background: var(--s2);
  border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px;
  font-size: 11px;
}
.log-item.blocked { border-color: rgba(248,113,113,.25); opacity: .5 }
.log-caller  { font-weight: 700; color: var(--t1); flex: 1 }
.log-field   { color: var(--t2); flex: 1 }
.log-time    { color: var(--t3); font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10px; flex-shrink: 0 }
.log-block-btn {
  background: transparent; border: 1px solid var(--border);
  color: var(--t3); font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700;
  padding: 3px 9px; border-radius: 5px; cursor: pointer;
  transition: all .15s; flex-shrink: 0;
}
.log-block-btn:hover { border-color: var(--red); color: var(--red) }
.log-block-btn.blocked-state {
  border-color: rgba(248,113,113,.3); color: var(--red);
  background: rgba(248,113,113,.07);
}
.see-all-btn {
  width: 100%; margin-top: 10px;
  background: transparent; border: 1px solid var(--border);
  color: var(--t2); font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600;
  padding: 9px; border-radius: 8px; cursor: pointer;
  transition: all .15s; text-align: center;
}
.see-all-btn:hover { border-color: var(--violet); color: var(--violet) }

/* ── ANIMATIONS ── */
@keyframes fadeUp { from { opacity:0; transform:translateY(14px) } to { opacity:1; transform:translateY(0) } }
@keyframes glow   { 0%,100% { box-shadow:0 0 6px var(--cyan) } 50% { box-shadow:0 0 14px var(--cyan) } }

.profile-hero  { animation: fadeUp .5s ease both }
.section       { animation: fadeUp .5s ease both }
.section:nth-child(2) { animation-delay:.08s }
.section:nth-child(3) { animation-delay:.16s }
.section:nth-child(4) { animation-delay:.24s }

.nc-status.on { animation: glow 2.5s ease-in-out infinite }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- TOPBAR -->
<header class="topbar">
  <div class="brand">livere.ai</div>
  <nav class="nav-links">
    <a class="nav-link" href="#">여론 분석</a>
    <a class="nav-link" href="#">아젠다</a>
    <a class="nav-link active" href="#">내 페르소나</a>
    <a class="nav-link" href="#">피드</a>
  </nav>
  <div class="topbar-right">
    <div class="weight-pill">
      <span class="wp-label">여론 가중치</span>
      <span class="wp-val">×1.72</span>
    </div>
    <button class="settings-btn" onclick="location.href='privacy_control.html'">
      🔒 공개 정보 설정
    </button>
  </div>
</header>

<main class="page">

  <!-- ── PROFILE HERO ── -->
  <div class="profile-hero">

    <!-- 아바타 -->
    <div class="avatar-card">
      <div class="avatar-ring-wrap">
        <svg class="avatar-ring-svg" viewBox="0 0 110 110">
          <circle cx="55" cy="55" r="50" fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,.05)" stroke-width="6"/>
          <circle cx="55" cy="55" r="50" fill="none" stroke="#22d3ee" stroke-width="6"
            stroke-dasharray="314" stroke-dashoffset="88" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        </svg>
        <div class="avatar-face">🧑</div>
      </div>
      <div class="avatar-pct">
        프로필 완성도
        <strong>72%</strong>
      </div>
      <div class="avatar-name">김민준</div>
      <div class="avatar-sub">
        livere.ai 멤버 · 2024.03 가입<br>
        총 발언 <strong style="color:var(--t1)">1,847건</strong>
      </div>
      <div class="avatar-badges">
        <span class="badge verified">✓ 인증됨</span>
        <span class="badge pro">PRO</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 신원 정보 + 커리어 -->
    <div class="identity-card">
      <div class="ic-title">기본 신원 정보</div>

      <div class="identity-grid">
        <div class="id-item">
          <div class="id-label">국적</div>
          <div class="id-val"><span class="lit">대한민국</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="id-item">
          <div class="id-label">현 거주지</div>
          <div class="id-val"><span class="lit">서울 강남구</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="id-item">
          <div class="id-label">생년</div>
          <div class="id-val"><span class="lit">1988년생</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="id-item">
          <div class="id-label">성별</div>
          <div class="id-val"><span class="lit">남성</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="id-item">
          <div class="id-label">결혼 여부</div>
          <div class="id-val empty">미입력</div>
        </div>
        <div class="id-item">
          <div class="id-label">보유 자산 구간</div>
          <div class="id-val"><span class="lit">중상 (상위 25%)</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="ic-title" style="margin-top:8px">직업 이력 (Career Timeline)</div>
      <div class="career-timeline" id="careerTimeline"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- 가중치 카드 -->
    <div class="weight-card">
      <div class="wc-title">여론 보정 가중치</div>

      <div class="weight-total">
        <div class="wt-val">×1.72</div>
        <div class="wt-label">내 발언 1건 = 평균 1.72표</div>
      </div>

      <div id="weightRows"></div>

      <div class="weight-note">
        💡 채워진 항목만 보정에 반영. 미입력 항목은 기본값(×1.0) 적용.<br>
        하루 10건 초과 발언은 자동 감쇠.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ── 페르소나 속성 노드 ── -->
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-head">
      페르소나 속성 노드
      <span class="section-sub">불이 켜진 항목만 여론 분석 보정에 사용됩니다</span>
    </div>
    <div class="node-grid" id="nodeGrid"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- ── 관심사 + 아젠다 활동 ── -->
  <div class="two-col section">

    <div class="stat-card">
      <div class="section-head" style="margin-bottom:10px">관심사 태그</div>
      <div class="interest-wrap" id="interestWrap"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="stat-card">
      <div class="section-head" style="margin-bottom:10px">최근 아젠다 활동</div>
      <div class="agenda-list" id="agendaList"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ── 주변 영향도 ── -->
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-head">주변 영향도</div>
    <div class="stat-card">
      <div class="spider-row">
        <div class="spider-svg-wrap">
          <svg id="spiderSvg" viewBox="0 0 180 180" width="180" height="180"></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="inf-bars" id="infBars"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ── 데이터 접근 로그 (미니) ── -->
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-head">
      최근 데이터 접근 로그
